"title": "5490: refuge",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5490: refuge",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A safe retreat; a place of healing and renewal; also a stronghold from which to launch a counter-attack.</p>\n<h2>False refuges</h2>\n<h3>Flight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:9\">GEN 3:8–3:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7-Ps139:12\">PSA 139:7–139:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:15\">ISA 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:17\">ISA 28:17</a></p>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9\">ISA 44:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:31\">DEU 32:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:37-Deut32:38\">DEU 32:37–32:38</a></p>\n<h3>Human support</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5\">JER 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7-Ps20:8\">PSA 20:7–20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:4\">PSA 142:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1-Isa30:2\">ISA 30:1–30:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">ZEC 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>False confidence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:14\">JER 6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:10-Ezek13:12\">EZK 13:10–13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:26-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:26–7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:17\">REV 6:15–6:17</a></p>\n<h2>God alone is the true refuge of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:32\">2SA 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:31\">PSA 18:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:6-Ps62:7\">PSA 62:6–62:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:32\">ROM 8:31–8:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:7\">PHP 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Pictures to describe God as a refuge</h2>\n<h3>A fortress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:7\">PSA 46:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:8\">PSA 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:3\">PSA 48:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:16\">PSA 59:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:16\">PSA 59:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:3\">PSA 71:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:2\">PSA 91:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:1-Ps144:3\">PSA 144:1–144:3</a></p>\n<h3>A rock</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:2-2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:2–22:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:24\">GEN 49:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15\">DEU 32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:47\">2SA 22:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:2\">PSA 31:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:22\">PSA 94:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>A shade</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1\">PSA 91:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5\">PSA 121:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:3\">SNG 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4-Isa25:5\">ISA 25:4–25:5</a></p>\n<h3>Sheltering wings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:10-Deut32:11\">DEU 32:10–32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:12\">RUT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">PSA 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7\">PSA 36:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a></p>\n<h3>A shield</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:29\">DEU 33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31\">2SA 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:3\">PSA 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5\">PRO 30:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:16\">EPH 6:16</a></p>\n<h3>A tower</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:3\">PSA 61:3</a></p>\n<h2>Cities of refuge</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:11\">NUM 35:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:41-Deut4:43\">DEU 4:41–4:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:1-Deut19:13\">DEU 19:1–19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh20:1-Josh20:9\">JOS 20:1–20:9</a></p>",
